What is the average quality of life score for customers under the payer name Blue Cross Blue Shield?
answers:
SELECT AVG(q.qols_avg) AS average_quality_of_life_score
FROM payers p
JOIN payer_transitions pt ON p.id = pt.payer
JOIN patients pa ON pt.patient = pa.id
JOIN patient_expenses pe ON pa.id = pe.patient_id
JOIN careplans c ON pa.id = c.patient
JOIN observations o ON pa.id = o.patient
JOIN conditions con ON pa.id = con.patient
JOIN procedures pr ON pa.id = pr.patient
JOIN claims cl ON pa.id = cl.patientid
JOIN providers pro ON cl.providerid = pro.id
JOIN encounters e ON cl.id = e.payer
JOIN organizations org ON e.organization = org.id
JOIN immunizations i ON pa.id = i.patient
JOIN allergies a ON pa.id = a.patient
JOIN supplies s ON pa.id = s.patient
JOIN medications m ON pa.id = m.patient
JOIN devices d ON pa.id = d.patient
JOIN imaging_studies im ON pa.id = im.patient
JOIN payer_transitions pt2 ON pa.id = pt2.patient
JOIN payers p2 ON pt2.payer = p2.id
JOIN claims_transactions ct ON cl.id = ct.claimid
JOIN providers pro2 ON ct.providerid = pro2.id
WHERE p.name = 'Blue Cross Blue Shield';

What is the average quality of life score for customers under the payer name NO_INSURANCE?
answers:
SELECT AVG(q.qols_avg) AS average_quality_of_life
FROM payers p
JOIN payer_transitions pt ON p.id = pt.payer
JOIN patients pa ON pt.patient = pa.id
JOIN patient_expenses pe ON pa.id = pe.patient_id
JOIN careplans c ON pa.id = c.patient
JOIN observations o ON pa.id = o.patient
JOIN conditions co ON pa.id = co.patient
JOIN procedures pr ON pa.id = pr.patient
JOIN claims cl ON pa.id = cl.patientid
JOIN providers pr ON cl.providerid = pr.id
JOIN organizations org ON pr.organization = org.id
JOIN immunizations i ON pa.id = i.patient
JOIN allergies a ON pa.id = a.patient
JOIN encounters e ON a.encounter = e.id
JOIN supplies s ON pa.id = s.patient
JOIN devices d ON pa.id = d.patient
JOIN medications m ON pa.id = m.patient
JOIN imaging_studies im ON pa.id = im.patient
JOIN observations o2 ON pa.id = o2.patient
JOIN conditions co2 ON pa.id = co2.patient
JOIN procedures pr2 ON pa.id = pr2.patient
JOIN claims cl2 ON pa.id = cl2.patientid
JOIN providers pr2 ON cl2.providerid = pr2.id
JOIN organizations org2 ON pr2.organization = org2.id
JOIN immunizations i2 ON pa.id = i2.patient
JOIN allergies a2 ON pa.id = a2.patient
JOIN encounters e2 ON a2.encounter = e2.id
WHERE p.name = 'NO_INSURANCE';

question: What is the average quality of life score for customers under the payer name Blue Cross Blue Shield?
answers:
SELECT AVG(q.qols_avg) AS average_quality_of_life_score
FROM payers p
JOIN payer_transitions pt ON p.id = pt.payer
JOIN patient_expenses pe ON pt.patient = pe.patient_id
JOIN patients pa ON pe.patient_id = pa.id
JOIN careplans c ON pa.id = c.patient
JOIN observations o ON c.encounter = o.encounter
JOIN conditions co ON o.encounter = co.encounter
JOIN devices d ON co.encounter = d.encounter
JOIN immunizations i ON d.encounter = i.encounter
JOIN procedures pr ON i.encounter = pr.encounter
JOIN providers pro ON pr.encounter = pro.encounters
JOIN organizations org ON pro.organization = org.id
JOIN claims cl ON pro.id = cl.providerid
JOIN claims_transactions ct ON cl.id = ct.claimid
JOIN supplies s ON ct.encounter = s.encounter
JOIN allergies a ON s.encounter = a.encounter
JOIN payer_transitions pt2 ON a.patient = pt2.patient
JOIN payers p2 ON pt2.payer = p2.id
JOIN patients pa2 ON pt2.patient = pa2.id
JOIN careplans c2 ON pa2.id = c2.patient
JOIN observations o2 ON c2.encounter = o2.encounter
JOIN conditions co2 ON o2.encounter = co2.encounter
JOIN devices d2 ON co2.encounter = d2.encounter
JOIN immunizations i2 ON d2.encounter = i2.encounter
JOIN procedures pr2 ON i2.encounter = pr2.encounter
JOIN providers pro2 ON pr2.encounter = pro2.encounters
JOIN organizations org2 ON pro2.organization = org2.id
JOIN claims cl2 ON pro2.id = cl2.providerid
JOIN claims_transactions ct2 ON cl2.id = ct2.claimid
JOIN supplies s2 ON ct2.encounter = s2.encounter
JOIN allergies a2 ON s2.encounter = a2.encounter
JOIN payer_transitions pt3 ON a2.patient = pt3.patient
JOIN payers p3 ON pt3.payer = p3.id
JOIN patient_expenses pe2 ON pt3.patient = pe2.patient_id
JOIN observations o3 ON pe2.patient_id = o3.patient
JOIN conditions co3 ON o3.encounter = co3.encounter
JOIN devices d3 ON co3.encounter = d3.encounter
JOIN immunizations i3 ON d3.encounter = i3.encounter
JOIN procedures pr3 ON i3.encounter = pr3.encounter
JOIN providers pro3 ON pr3.encounter = pro3.encounters
JOIN organizations org3 ON pro3.organization = org3.id
WHERE p2.name = 'Blue Cross Blue Shield';

question: What is the average quality of life score for customers under the payer with ID 26aab0cd-6aba-3e1b-ac5b-05c8867e762c?
What is the average quality of life score for customers under the payer name Humana?
answers:
SELECT AVG(q.qols_avg) AS average_quality_of_life_score
FROM payers p
JOIN patient_expenses pe ON p.id = pe.payer_id
JOIN patients pt ON pe.patient_id = pt.id
JOIN careplans cp ON pt.id = cp.patient
JOIN observations o ON cp.encounter = o.encounter
JOIN conditions c ON o.encounter = c.encounter
JOIN payer_transitions pt ON pt.patient = pt.patient
JOIN organizations org ON pt.id = org.id
JOIN providers pr ON org.id = pr.organization
JOIN procedures pr ON pr.patient = pr.patient
JOIN claims cl ON cl.patientid = pt.id
JOIN claims_transactions ct ON cl.id = ct.claimid
WHERE p.name = 'Humana';
